# 從頭再嚟  
(pos:成語／動詞短語)  
<explanation>  
yue:由最開始嘅一步重新開始，重新做起（通常喺失敗、出錯或想重新開始時使用）  
eng:to start all over again from the beginning; to begin again from scratch  

<eg>  
yue:呢單生意搞砸咗，唯有從頭再嚟。 (ni1 daan1 saang1 jing6 ga2 zaak3 zo2, jau4 jyu6 cong4 tau4 zoi3 lai4.)  
eng:The business deal fell through, so we had no choice but to start all over again.  

yue:你寫錯咗段開頭，不如從頭再嚟啦！ (nei5 se2 co3 zo2 do1 hoi1 tau3, bat1 jyu4 cong4 tau4 zoi3 lai4 laa3!)  
eng:You messed up the opening paragraph—might as well start from the beginning!  

yue:呢首歌我唱錯咗幾句，可唔可以從頭再嚟一次？ (ni1 sau2 gung1 ngo5 coeng3 co3 zo2 ge2 geoi1, ho2 bat1 ho2 ji5 cong4 tau4 zoi3 lai4 jat1 ci3?)  
eng:I messed up a few lines singing this song—can we do it again from the start? [end of text]


